name: The sanctity of love
description:
Holy love

We can come and cry tonight
Your holy love, come to our guests

Revive my feeling of being the butler of you
Let's try to drink a sip of pain

The house is lively, fire and light dance
Wow, it's good to burn every moment

Loop my ring into my flesh
my Lord ! Let's dance

I'm waiting for you to polish me this time
Or give me a human face as a gift

Hazrat Eshgh came and the house of the heart was warmed
Can we stay and get angry? !!!
